{"tid":1415853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚]之後的行動方向","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T14:41:03.000Z","uid":258095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"267ca2667c5c07d094a8a65158f8ae7963b7b823","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"首先 我認為開多區戰線雖然可以分散警力<br />\n遍地開花 但係都有唔少嘅缺點<br />\n<br />\n第一 有啲區嘅手足明顯經驗不足 裝備不足<br />\n好似今日荃灣區依邊 照我所睇 <br />\n現場有好多 經驗不足嘅人<br />\n成日被人帶風向同埋跑住走<br />\n令到前線失去支援和逃跑過程容易引起混亂<br />\n出現人踩人嘅機會<br />\n因此偶爾嘅集中戰線令抗爭新手獲取經驗<br />\n<br />\n第二 圍左咁多日嘅警署 <br />\n係時候到準返個政權<br />\n圍或者衝一啲更有意義嘅地方<br />\n好似之前嘅立法會同中聯辦一樣 <br />\n而依啲地方通常都派重兵<br />\n同埋唔係個個區都有<br />\n因此要集中戰線 <br />\n而去嘅地點大家可以討論下<br />\n<br />\n題外話 大家一直提倡嘅be humble<br />\n係今日早段的確做到 好有禮貌咁講唔該<br />\n叫人唔好亂影相 但去到中後段<br />\n義士嘅腎上腺素上升時 似乎控制唔到<br />\n希望大家可以互相提點下<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\n我都會發表下自己淺見"},{"pid":"ce65da4567eea369bd369f544c473d7fc8f67cb1","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afe38184d8ab144b67b686c43e0217d004abc809","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"另外未來嘅記者會<br />\n希望可以向大眾解釋<br />\n我哋依場運動並唔係一昧想向港獨發展"},{"pid":"ff6126fd94744d3e4609fb245cd05ed0d3bba6b2","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39e93be524d7689b317d8e17c4dcdedccf541a08","tid":1415853,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:19:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"111f0150c288ea82e73fb21ee06d19bf6eedd739","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:22:07.000Z","msg":"正負評之餘都想大家討論"},{"pid":"abfe9a5649d6857b297bf61015f73210fb76ca35","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"討論"},{"pid":"b0d9e6ebb30ccf568b1c39cae456f18e2722078f","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:31:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98fce70ca955d9d947dc676009318c773980498c","tid":1415853,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"拋磚之後...縱火？<br />\n全面升級"},{"pid":"b4bc152bb835cbf1a9a540566c8c3cfa986f3ee9","tid":1415853,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣補血</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8cad75d478ecb4d21cab2564f1572962fa040188","tid":1415853,"uid":258095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fce70ca955d9d947dc676009318c773980498c","tid":1415853,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"拋磚之後...縱火？<br />\n全面升級"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"我個拋磚係引玉"}]}